Fixed IllegalStateException: Can not perform this action after onSaveInstanceState. Put a try catch block and ignore the error
Added CardView to RecyclerView and animation on Recyclerview
Added full functionality favorite in both Fragments, list and map

Fixed problem with Loader in MapFragment. As this fragment is not the default fragment in ViewPager it doen't call onStart until the user switch from list to map fragment. The Loader flows is dependant on the onStart method of the fragment. solution:setUserVisibilityHint(true) in map fragment, so that onStart loads, and thus Loader loads also.
Fixed: Drawer freeze solved and GPS disconnection:place .disconnect() after stopLocationUpdates in onPause(). Implemented setFragment(0) refresh time.
Fixed loading after Setting screen. Added setUserVisibilityHint to ListTabFragment. Refactored getMapFragment in MainActivity
